name: Nari
dialog: P_name! Can you take a pretty picture of me?

name: 주인공
dialog: Sure, what kind of picture do you want?

name: Nari
dialog: Take a picture of me brushing my teeth.

name: 주인공
dialog: You want me to take a picture of you brushing your teeth?

name: Nari
dialog: Yeah, it's for a teeth-brushing photo contest.
비고: 주인공의 이를 확대해서 보여준다. 누렇고, 치석이 껴있고, 음식물도 그득함. 어금니 쪽엔 충치도(앞니와 입을 벌린 모습 둘 다 보여줌)

name: Nari
dialog: Yeah, it's an event to promote how important healthy teeth are. That's why I want to participate too.

name: 주인공
dialog: Now that I think about it, your teeth look clean and healthy.

name: 주인공
dialog: I forget to brush my teeth sometimes,

name: 주인공
dialog: so they are not always clean and sometimes hurt.

name: Nari
dialog: They say that brushing your teeth is the foundation of healthy teeth.

name: Nari
dialog: You need to brush your teeth well to prevent cavities.

name: Nari
dialog: I studied about healthy teeth to participate in this teeth-brushing photo contest.

name: Nari
dialog: Well, you need to learn the right way to brush your teeth and then brush them well.

name: Nari
dialog: I'll tell you what I learned.

name: Nari
dialog: You need to have the right brushing habits from a young age.
